RT:

Change existing Task's priority => Task should be moved to correct spot on peer.
Create new Task => Task should appear on peer.
Change newly created Task's priority => Task should be moved to the correct spot on peer.
The current resource has been removed by a peer => A modal error dialog should appear.
A peer changes the start date of a sprint => The change should be reflected in the order of sprints in the index view.
Change remaining_time on task => The change should be reflected on the sprint view.

Misc:

Change sprint range => The Stories' remaining times should be recalculated in the view.
Open a non existing resource => A blank page should appear with an modal error dialog.